&lt;div&gt;The Innovation Architect is the strategic and architectural layer of a MOST engagement. They run discovery, diagnose how teams actually work today, design the governance and collaboration infrastructure to support where the customer is heading, and build the roadmap for how 240 hours get used across the year. They also own AI workflow advisory, helping customers move from ad hoc Miro usage to intelligent, repeatable collaboration systems.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;This role is open because the program is growing and the complexity of enterprise accounts has outpaced what CSMs and Technical Architects can absorb on top of their core scope. The right candidate has a consulting background, is fluent in collaboration platforms, and is comfortable running live discovery with a skeptical CTO and a frustrated Product Lead at the same time. They own delivery quality from day one.&lt;/div&gt;
