&lt;p&gt;We are the Solutions Engineering team at Miro Japan. We play a critical role in bridging the gap between technical innovation and business needs. Our mission is to be solutions champions for our customers’ and partners’ requirements, bringing the product to life within the technically complex environments of our largest Enterprise customers.&lt;/p&gt;
