&lt;p&gt;Miro is looking for a visionary Staff&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Product Designer&lt;/strong&gt; to lead the charge for our &lt;strong&gt;Prototypes&lt;/strong&gt; product. This isn’t just about refining a feature; it’s about defining the future of how millions of people bring their ideas to life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a key leader within the Canvas Modes stream, you will lead the long-term design strategy for Prototyping at Miro. We are looking for an&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;AI Native designer &lt;/strong&gt;-&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;someone who doesn’t just see AI as a feature but as a fundamental shift in the product development process and ultimately, a massive opportunity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be tasked with shaping not just where Miro’s Prototype offering should be, but where it is going - ensuring we aren&#39;t just keeping pace with the market, but setting it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and drive the North Star for Miro Prototyping. You’ll articulate a vision that disrupts the norms and looks where the market is going.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a tireless innovator in the AI space. You will explore how generative AI can collapse the gap between a rough sketch and full functioning app.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Approach the product with an entrepreneurial spirit and sense of ownership. You’ll navigate ambiguity, build lean experiments, and treat the Prototyping mode as your own startup within Miro.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage your deep understanding of the design tool landscape to create a best-in-class experience that rivals any competitor while maintaining Miro’s ease of use and considering our other suite of formats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Product and Engineering to solve complex technical challenges around AI quality, discoverability, and the seamless transition between the ‘infinite canvas’ and ‘Prototypes Focus Mode’.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set the bar for design excellence at Miro, mentoring other designers and contributing to the evolution of our design systems and internal tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
