&lt;li&gt;Strong account expansion skills (new business, strategic territory &amp;amp; account planning, cross functional team-selling).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of exceeding sales quotas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills in English &amp;amp; German.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have the ability to build rapport and relationships with senior clients incl. Business Decision Makers and C-Level.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a great attitude that can maneuver through ambiguity and ability to work and collaborative with a growing team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a results-oriented individual who is excited by the prospect of fueling the continued growth and success of Miro by growing our sales pipeline. You have a “can do” attitude and are relentless in pursuing goals and solving problems.&lt;/li&gt;
